                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="T47n1998A-start">
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b14.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:36:43.139+09:00">Vice-Minister Zeng's¹ Letter to Dahui</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s1" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:37:25.49+09:00">While stationed in the city of Changsha²</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s2" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:37:43.029+09:00">I received a letter from Master Yuanwu Keqin.³</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s3" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:38:41.511+09:00">In it he mentioned you, saying that although you began your training under him relatively late in life⁴</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s4" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:38:48.365+09:00">your attainments were extraordinary.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s5" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:40:23.942+09:00">In the eight years since then</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s6" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:40:59.711+09:00">I have often thought of you, always holding you in the deepest respect and</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s7" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:41:02.442+09:00">regretting my inability to directly hear even just a portion [of your wisdom].</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s8" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:42:15.43+09:00">x From the time I was a child I have aspired to the Way,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s9" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:42:22.901+09:00">seeking guidance from wise teachers⁵ on This Matter.⁶</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s10" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:42:30.559+09:00">However, since turning twenty and reaching the age of majority</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s11" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:42:31.513+09:00">I have been occupied with family life and official duties,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s12" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:43:57.233+09:00">and thus unable to devote myself fully to Chan practice.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s13" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:44:12.972+09:00">To this very day I have been squandering my time in this manner.  Although I am now advanced in years</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s14" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:44:20.779+09:00">I have learned nothing, a source of constant shame and regret.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s15" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:50:09.144+09:00">x Nevertheless, my determination to seek the Way and aspiration for the truth</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s16" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:50:42.485+09:00">are not based on frivolous notions.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s17" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:51:17.878+09:00">The way I see it, should I fail to awaken then that's that,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s18" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:53:05.284+09:00">but having set out to awaken I must strive to attain the very same place realized by the ancient masters, the realm of ultimate repose.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s19" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:52:57.058+09:00"> My determination to do this has never lapsed for an instant,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s20" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:52:41.272+09:00">but I recognize that I have not been sufficiently focused in my efforts.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s21" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:52:45.928+09:00">One could say I am "great in aspiration but slight in ability."</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s22" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:54:01.961+09:00">Some time ago</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s23" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:54:03.694+09:00">Master Yuanwu, in response to my earnest entreaty,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s24" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:54:12.844+09:00">granted me his six-part "Dharma Talks."⁷</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s25" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:54:20.007+09:00">They begin by pointing directly to This Matter,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s26" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:58:17.03+09:00">and later recommend practice with steady awareness on the koans "Yunmen's 'Mount Sumeru"⁸ and "Zhaozhou's 'Drop it!'"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s27" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:59:02.679+09:00">Master Yuanwu writes that</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s28" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:59:10.843+09:00">if these koans are kept constantly in mind,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s29" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:59:12.125+09:00">in due time one will without fail enter the gate of awakening.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s30" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:59:33.864+09:00">Despite his grandmotherly kindness¹⁰ in offering these instructions,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s31" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T21:59:36.901+09:00">I was too dull and set in my ways to accomplish anything.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s32" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:01:23.097+09:00">Fortunately, I have now fulfilled all of my family obligations</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s33" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:01:24.313+09:00">and am able to live at leisure, free of encumbrances.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s34" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:03:13.396+09:00">This is the time to apply the whip to myself and revive my original aspiration.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s35" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:03:15.171+09:00">I only regret that I have not been able to receive your personal guidance.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s36" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:03:22.973+09:00">I have already described the misspent years of my life.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s37" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:03:39.665+09:00">Please look into my mind and</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s38" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:04:13.396+09:00">provide me with detailed instruction and advice.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s39" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:04:15.536+09:00">How should I practice in daily life?</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s40" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:04:31.196+09:00">I wish to accord directly with the Original Ground</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s41" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:04:39.52+09:00">and to avoid straying down side paths.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s42" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:05:13.942+09:00">In writing to you like this</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s43" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:05:27.403+09:00">I have revealed my many missteps,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s44" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:06:56.592+09:00">but I am expressing myself in all sincerity and thus must not conceal anything.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s45" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:06:58.622+09:00">I beg your understanding.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916b1501.s46" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-26T22:06:59.688+09:00">With best wishes.</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916c0601.s14" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-27T11:12:05.352+09:00">bb</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#T47n1998A_CBETA_025-0916c0601.s15" xml:lang="en" resp="#chris" modified="2025-02-27T11:12:25.133+09:00">cc</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
